# Validation Matrix Enforcement

## Must
- Map each change to required test classes and active phase gates.
- Enforce metric conformance against thresholds from `docs/pipeline/validation-metrics.md`.
- Require determinism, resilience, soak, perf, and KPI tests when applicable by phase.
- Block promotion when any required metric or scenario gate fails.

## Must Not
- Do not duplicate threshold values in ad-hoc scripts unless generated from source docs.
- Do not claim pass status without per-scenario pass/fail output.

## Required Evidence
- Matrix report showing required vs executed checks and results.
